How to use ellip3d

1. compile

1.1 serial mode
   step 1) edit main.cpp for your specific simulation type and parameters
   step 2) edit makefile to exclude OPENMP from OPTION.
   step 3) make
   step 4) copy ellip3d, main.cpp, parameter.cpp to your simulation directory

1.2 openmp mode
   step 1) edit main.cpp for your specific simulation type and parameters
   step 2) edit makefile to include OPENMP for OPTION
   step 3) make
   step 4) copy ellip3d, main.cpp, parameter.cpp to your simulation directory

2. run

2.1 serial mode
./ellip3d or ./ellip3d > tmp &

2.2 openmp mode
export OMP_NUM_THREADS=6
./ellip3d or ./ellip3d > tmp &
